CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773668263
OL,3,CFormer MP Phil Woolas dies aged 66,
OL,4,Cfamily announce
OL,6,F"Before entering Parliament, Phil was
OL,7,FNUS president, TV producer and GMB
OL,8,Funion communications director.
OL,10,F"He served as MP for Oldham East and
OL,11,FSaddleworth from 1997 to 2010, and a
OL,12,Fminister in both Tony Blair and Gordon
OL,13,FBrown's governments ` appointed
OL,14,Fsuccessively: whip, deputy leader of
OL,15,Fthe Commons, local government
OL,16,Fminister, environment minister and
OL,17,Fimmigration minister."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUyD@VO]
