PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773668263
OL,3,CFormer MP Phil Woolas dies aged 66,
OL,4,Cfamily announce
OL,6,FIn a notable moment of his career at
OL,7,Fthe Home Office, Mr Woolas was on one
OL,8,Foccasion confronted by actor Joanna
OL,9,FLumley during a live press conference
OL,10,Fto make concessions over the rights of
OL,11,FGurkhas to remain in the UK.
OL,13,FThe statement from his friends and
OL,14,Ffamily added: "From 2011 onwards, Phil
OL,15,Fset up and ran his own political and
OL,16,Frisk consultancy.
OL,26,@vD@OOU
