PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1773668263
OL,3,CFormer MP Phil Woolas dies aged 66,
OL,4,Cfamily announce
OL,6,F"For more than 25 years, Phil was the
OL,7,Fchair of The Ace Centre, an Oldham
OL,8,Fcharity helping people with
OL,9,Fcommunication difficulties, that he
OL,10,Fled to become a national charity
OL,11,Fleader in assistive technology for
OL,12,Fseverely disabled people."
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@ZO]
